170
00:09:25,390 --> 00:09:30,660
Well, between me and a guy with talent,
I guess all-nighters don't mean the same.

171
00:09:30,990 --> 00:09:33,050
Hiroshi, what's "talent"?

172
00:09:33,670 --> 00:09:36,160
It's when a guy can do anything
with just a little effort,

173
00:09:36,160 --> 00:09:39,400
