175
00:09:43,300 --> 00:09:45,440
Hey, who'd you hear that from?!

176
00:09:46,010 --> 00:09:47,670
Woohoo!

177
00:09:47,670 --> 00:09:49,520
I feel like workin' hard, too!

178
00:09:50,090 --> 00:09:51,360
