you've gotten to be a burden.

228
00:12:07,240 --> 00:12:09,080
I've been a burden?

229
00:12:09,610 --> 00:12:14,520
Besides, I plan to study seriously
for my exams from now on.

230
00:12:14,520 --> 00:12:20,120
I'd like to try following your example,
and make a proper effort.

231
00:12:20,120 --> 00:12:24,780
