246
00:13:05,930 --> 00:13:10,680
Nanatsutake Hospital

247
00:13:10,680 --> 00:13:14,680
Handa Sei
Private Room

248
00:13:11,190 --> 00:13:14,680
Heatstroke, sleep deprivation, poor appetite...

249
00:13:15,460 --> 00:13:17,420
