255
00:13:28,370 --> 00:13:31,030
Yeah, I'm hooked up to an IV, so I'll be fine.

256
00:13:31,360 --> 00:13:32,680
Huh...

257
00:13:32,990 --> 00:13:34,740
Does it hurt worse'n a shot?

258
00:13:36,610 --> 00:13:38,000
I'm not sure...

259
00:13:38,240 --> 00:13:39,690
Well, Sensei.

260
00:13:39,690 --> 00:13:43,030
We'll fetch what you need
for stayin' the night here.

261
00:13:43,030 --> 00:13:44,770
Uh, right.

262
00:13:44,770 --> 00:13:47,680
If you need anything,
feel free to call on Iku-chan.

263
00:13:48,000 --> 00:13:51,570
